Tony Sirico https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tony_Sirico 0 Genaro Anthony Sirico Jr. (born July 29, 1942) is an American actor, best known for his role as Paul "Paulie Walnuts" Gualtieri in The Sopranos and various roles in the films of Woody Allen.
